 taking Meta to small claims court to get some kind of response to their complaints. Engadget spoke with five individuals who have sued Meta in small claims court over the last two years. In three cases, the plaintiffs were able to restore access to at least one lost account, but all eventually got the attention of Meta&#39;s legal team.</p><p> The company has argued that it is not liable for more than $100 in damages according to its terms of service. However, some plaintiffs were awarded thousands of dollars — which still might pale compared to lost earnings for those whose businesses revolve around their Facebook or Instagram presence. We chart the mixed results of these users and Meta&#39;s logic in giving them so much attention.</p><p> — 马特·史密斯</p><h3 id="jump-link-the-biggest-stories-you-might-have-missed">您可能错过的最重要的故事</h3><h3 id="jump-link-"></h3><p><a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-ssds-140014262.html">2024 年最佳 SSD</a></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-reportedly-has-plans-for-a-thinner-iphone-macbook-pro-and-apple-watch-171137550.html">Apple reportedly has plans for a thinner iPhone, MacBook Pro, and Apple Watch</a></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/more-than-1000-students-pledge-not-to-work-at-google-and-amazon-due-to-project-nimbus-042439081.html">由于 Nimbus 项目，超过 1000 名学生承诺不再在谷歌和亚马逊工作</a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-house-will-open-two-locations-in-texas-and-pennsylvania-in-2025-213033751.html">Netflix House 将于 2025 年在德克萨斯州和宾夕法尼亚州开设两家地点</a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-webb-telescopes-dazzling-nebula-image-supports-a-long-held-theory-210229206.html">韦伯望远镜令人眼花缭乱的星云图像支持了一个长期存在的理论</a></p><p><em>​​您可以每天将这些报告直接发送到您的收件箱。</em><a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/about/newsletter/"><em>在这里订阅！</em></a></p><p></p><h2 id="jump-link-amazon-says-its-cut-down-on-its-plastic-air-pillows"> <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-says-its-cut-down-on-those-plastic-air-pillows-in-packages-222953642.html">Amazon says it&#39;s cut down on its plastic air pillows</a></h2><h3 id="jump-link-popping-them-makes-me-jump"> Popping them makes me jump.</h3><h3 id="jump-link-"></h3><p> You may have already noticed, but Amazon says it&#39;s reduced its use of plastic airbags included with its packages, shifting to compostable paper filler in most cases. It plans to eliminate using them by the end of the year. It&#39;s a move in the right direction: In 2021, the nonprofit ocean conservation group Oceana estimated that the waste produced from plastic air pillows alone “would circle the Earth more than 600 times.”</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-says-its-cut-down-on-those-plastic-air-pillows-in-packages-222953642.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p><p></p><h2 id="jump-link-a-remastered-beyond-good-and-evil-arrives-next-week"> <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-beyond-good-and-evil-remaster-will-be-released-next-week-for-real-230001749.html">A remastered Beyond Good and Evil arrives next week</a></h2><h3 id="jump-link-but-wheres-that-sequel"> But where&#39;s that sequel?</h3> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/the-beyond-good-and-evil-remaster-will-be-released-next-week-for-real-230001749.html"><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-06/e1de1060-2fa9-11ef-b5cb-154b15c9ca4a" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-06/e1de1060-2fa9-11ef-b5cb-154b15c9ca4a" style="height:380px;width:675px;" alt="TMA" data-uuid="52e7e38e-c9a3-371d-a8bb-de2466af048c"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">育碧</div></figure></a><p>Ubisoft has released a trailer for its remake of the cult classic game Beyond Good and Evil, adding that it will launch on June 25. The understated cult hit has been upgraded to 4K and 60FPS – it was initially released on the PS2, so you&#39;ll see the difference. It will be available on PC, PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Nintendo Switch, Xbox One, and Xbox Series X/S, with physical copies going on sale next month, too. What about the sequel that has been <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2008-05-28-beyond-good-and-evil-2-revealed-at-ubidays-2008.html">revealed</a> , teased,<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2016-01-30-beyond-good-and-evil-2.html">promised</a> , and… <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-06-14-beyond-good-evil-2-gameplay-demo-e3.html">seen</a> (by me!)?无话可说。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-beyond-good-and-evil-remaster-will-be-released-next-week-for-real-230001749.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a> </p><p></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2 id="jump-link-the-us-will-ban-sales-of-kaspersky-antivirus-software"> <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-us-will-ban-sales-of-kaspersky-antivirus-software-next-month-205106837.html">The US will ban sales of Kaspersky antivirus software</a></h2><h3 id="jump-link-after-years-of-scrutiny-over-the-russian-companys-government-ties"> After years of scrutiny over the Russian company&#39;s government ties.</h3><h3 id="jump-link-"></h3><p>拜登政府已采取全面行动，禁止卡巴斯基实验室向美国客户销售其防病毒产品。一位消息人士告诉<em>路透社</em>，该公司与俄罗斯政府的关系使其构成安全风险。卡巴斯基在报告中的一份声明中补充说，其活动不会威胁国家安全，并将寻求法律选择。 FCC 在 2022 年将卡巴斯基列入构成不可接受安全风险的公司名单，而早在 2017 年，美国联邦机构就禁止卡巴斯基产品。从 7 月开始，该公司无法向新客户销售产品。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-us-will-ban-sales-of-kaspersky-antivirus-software-next-month-205106837.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-how-small-claims-court-became-metas-customer-service-hotline-111555251.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-mor