<ins>PlayStation Stars</ins></a> ，这是一项奖励您完成某些游戏任务的数字收藏品的忠诚度计划。它也不是已经不复存在的<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2010-10-27-playstation-rewards.html"><ins>PlayStation 奖励计划</ins></a>，该计划为最贪婪的 PlayStation 游戏玩家提供 PSN 奖励。它将终止通过索尼和 PlayStation 品牌的 Visa 信用卡提供的索尼奖励计划。</p><p>该公司<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.rewards.sony.com/faq"><ins>更新了常见问题解答</ins></a>以及<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.rewards.sony.com/terms.html"><ins>条款和条件</ins></a>页面，以反映其将于 2024 年 12 月 31 日关闭索尼奖励网站和移动应用程序，并且将不再接受新会员加入该计划，立即生效。从现在到新年前夜，现有的索尼和 PlayStation 持卡人仍然可以通过该应用程序兑换积分、访问其帐户以及提交奖励积分和购买积分申请表。但是，7 月 21 日之后，他们无法通过邮寄方式发送实物奖励积分和信用请求积分。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>此外，会员无法再通过优惠或合作伙伴优惠赚取积分，也无法将其帐户链接到 Sony Store 或 Movies Anywhere。 Sony Rewards 客户服务将于 2025 年 2 月 14 日停止运营。就 Sony 和 PlayStation 信用卡而言，Comenity Bank 将适时联系持卡人了解信用卡计划的变更，但持卡人可以继续使用直至December 31.</p><p>索尼奖励计划于 2017 年推出，允许您通过索尼或 PlayStation 信用卡累积足够的积分来兑换仅来自索尼品牌的商品。乍一看，用积分兑换 PlayStation 游戏似乎是一项很大的福利，但兑换过程并不灵活，而且购买的年利率高达 27.99%。微软去年推出的<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/forget-cash-back-microsofts-xbox-mastercard-exclusively-earns-game-discounts-185141446.html"><ins>Xbox 万事达卡</ins></a>也存在同样的问题，但年利率可能为 20.99%、26.99% 或 31.99%，具体取决于您的余额。另外，没有现金返还。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/sony-will-terminate-its-sony-rewards-program-224538912.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/sony-will-terminate-its-sony-rewards-program-224538912.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 7d6c96da-246f-43c7-b464-216c2dccda1f </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Cristina Alexander]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 20 Jun 2024 22:45:38 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1718922950</ingested><modified> 2024-06-20T22:35:56+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Game Consoles]]></category><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Cristina Alexander]]></category><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-06%2F2a55b3c0-2f55-11ef-a7fb-efe9bcd5f2da&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=fdf2219de8ab7a090b2d31c167d88e741b6acebc" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-06%2F2a55b3c0-2f55-11ef-a7fb-efe9bcd5f2da&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=ddec57e02b001e3a7530cc93100f5adbe81896c8" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Sony]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[PlayStation credit card]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[PlayStation credit card]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Amazon says it’s cut down on those plastic air pillows in packages]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>您知道您在亚马逊购买的较易碎的商品中的那些小塑料气囊，当您压碎它们时，它们会发出完美的爆裂声吗？亚马逊表示，它已经减少了它们的使用，并计划在今年年底前完全消除它们的使用。</p><p>这家电子商务巨头在<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.aboutamazon.com/news/sustainability/amazon-replaces-plastic-air-pillows-in-packaging-north-america-us"><ins>其新闻博客</ins></a>上宣布，已将塑料气枕的使用量减少了 95%，并改用碎纸填充物。亚马逊还表示，计划在<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day-2024-deals-to-shop-ahead-of-prime-day-and-everything-we-know-about-the-summer-sale-110027526.html"><ins>Prime Day</ins></a>期间为“几乎所有”客户送货使用纸张填充器。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>该公司表示，其决定在其配送中心逐步停止使用塑料气垫，旨在消除不必要的浪费，并更多地关注使用回收材料。</p><p>塑料污染一直是我们环境中的一个令人担忧的问题，但由于亚马逊的迅速崛起，特别是在新冠疫情期间，塑料污染急剧增加。非营利性海洋保护组织<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://oceana.org/reports/amazon-report-2021/"><ins>Oceana</ins></a>在 2021 年发布的一项研究显示，亚马逊在 2020 年产生了 5.99 亿磅的塑料垃圾。该组织还估计，仅塑料气枕产生的垃圾就“可以绕地球 600 多圈”。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/amazon-says-its-cut-down-on-those- Plastic-air-pillows-in-packages-222953642.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/amazon-says-its-cut-down-on-those-plastic-air-pillows-in-packages-222953642.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 3278d980-7981-49c5-8ba7-84a4f6a18384 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Danny Gallagher]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 20 Jun 2024 22:29:54 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1718922594</ingested><modified> 2024-06-20T22:30:02+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Pollution & Waste]]></category><category><![CDATA[Conservation & Recycling]]></category><category><![CDATA[Environment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Nature & Environment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Danny Gallagher]]></category><media:content height="786" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-06%2F61f502a0-2f54-11ef-a7df-a4ef79631337&amp;resize=1400%2C786&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=28572b5a60d250a513023ad0bd85fc93d528ee30" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="786" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-06%2F61f502a0-2f54-11ef-a7df-a4ef79631337&amp;resize=1400%2C786&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=fe4c69c0cf79f6f4c8238f0eb3e5ab95d460dded" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Amazon]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Amazon Air Pillows]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Amazon Air Pillows]]></media:title></media:content></item></channel></rss>